Dion Wired is running a promotion on some of the latest and greatest smartphones, tech gadgets, and home appliances until 27 August. These promotional deals are available both online and in-store. The NEW Samsung Galaxy Note 10 and Note 10 Plus is currently available for pre-order. By pre-ordering, the Note 10 will only set you back R19,999 while the Note 10 Plus is priced at R22,999. The Samsung Note 10 and 10 Plus comes with a limited launch gift to the value of R3,500. In addition to this limited launch gift, customers who pre-order their Samsung Note 10 or 10 Plus on the Dion Wired website will also receive a FREE R3,500 Dion Wired gift card. This exclusive pre-order deal is available from 8-27 August only. Other great deals include a Dell Inspiron 15 3580 with biometrics enabled security features for only R7,999 – saving you R1,000 – and an EPSON EcoTank 3-in-1 colour printer for only R1,999 – saving you R900. You can view these and many other great deals that are available from Dion Wired below. To learn more, visit the Dion Wired online store. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-316467" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/epson.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="633" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/epson.jpg 755w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/epson-404x400.jpg 404w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/epson-435x430.jpg 435w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-316475" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/NutriBullet.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="644" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/NutriBullet.jpg 654w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/NutriBullet-398x400.jpg 398w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/NutriBullet-427x430.jpg 427w" sizes